								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="stat-card">
								<div class="stat-icon" style="background: rgba(250, 166, 26, 0.2);">
									<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FAA61A">
										<path d="M1 21h22L12 2 1 21zm12-3h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2v-4h2v4z"/>
